FBIS4-49912 "drchi092_j_94002" FBIS-CHI-94-092 Daily Report 6 May 1994 Latin America & Caribbean NPC Vice Chairman Meets With Argentine Defense Group NPC Vice Chairman Meets With Argentine Defense Group OW0605130894 Beijing XINHUA in English 0931 GMT 6 May 94 OW0605130894 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, May 6 (XINHUA) -- Ni Zhifu, vice-chairman of the Standing Committee of the Chinese National People's Congress (NPC), met with a delegation from the National Defense Committee (NDC) of Argentine Senate here this afternoon. The delegation, headed by Eduardo Pedro Vaca, NDC chairman of Argentine Senate, arrived here Wednesday [4 May] as guests of the NPC Foreign Affairs Committee. Zhu Liang, chairman of the NPC Foreign Affairs Committee, met with Vaca and his party and hosted a banquet in their honor here yesterday. Vaca and his party are also expected to travel to Dalian, Shanghai, Suzhou and Nanjing during their China visit.
